{"tid":1772924,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"政府真係好驚呢樣野","createTime":"2019-12-07T05:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T12:18:19.000Z","uid":169096,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"25a117fc026e82d600668ba31600b433d4ef3aba","tid":1772924,"uid":169096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係連儂牆</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">  近日成日派人清連儂牆，清文宣<br />\n仲要幾十防暴去守<br />\n琴日痴完嘅文宣今日就唔見咗 </span><br />\n佢地咁手快<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">  證明政府就係好怕我地團結<br />\n好怕啲資訊比更多人睇到<br />\n所以我地要比之前更加團結 </span><br />\n更加有策略<br />\n我地要進步！<br />\n各位手足不要鬆懈<br />\n貼文宣嘅兄弟都要小心<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">  <span style=\"color: red;\">  128維園見！  </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8b332c5d8f1f0908d121478517048dbfc1786059","tid":1772924,"uid":169096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:21:30.000Z","msg":"128維園見！"},{"pid":"39574f6763f16e5df3eb58ea54e9f5c6f8d63071","tid":1772924,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44bab755abdf585e0a1c0aa808a739e6b7d5390b","tid":1772924,"uid":18114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:24:19.000Z","msg":"問：政府究竟有幾多樣野驚過"},{"pid":"70066d6ef58d6de718651f6ec86b168b1f056873","tid":1772924,"uid":235015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:24:46.000Z","msg":"區選完各區直頭係兩三日就清一次"},{"pid":"15e9c1ea2b767965ebe405bbda9e0a5b37d01238","tid":1772924,"uid":169096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"128維園見！"},{"pid":"ea3b78a7070503146972b2392635fe6d6ecdc101","tid":1772924,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:25:17.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"0620b814bf70bed47f1ffce2fd4c5a7ca08db3d5","tid":1772924,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"